snippet.title: Call of Duty: Warzone Mobile | Launch Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The date is set! Gear up and get ready to drop in 🪂 🌎

Warzone Mobile deploys March 21st worldwide! Tag your squad and make sure you're ready for the fight with rewards by pre-registering now callofduty.com/warzonemobile. 

🌐 Pre-reg on Google Play or Pre-Order on the App Store for free now: https://www.callofduty.com/warzonemobile

Follow us for all the latest intel:
Facebook: https://facebook.com/CODWarzoneMobile/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WarzoneMobile
Instagram: https://instagram.com/codwarzonemobile/
